text: Terram quoque duorum aratruum in locis nominatis illicðæt Suiðhunincg lond æt Grafon aea.
Duas possessiunculas et tertiam dimediam, id est in nostra loquellaðridda half haga.
Ærest on easthealfe betwynan leage & elmanstede swa ofer scæt.
Oþ stænincgmearce, swa andlang dices west on burhrode.
East on stræte on<../images/tbar.gif>ealde þrymyrce lehwara, and denewara, and elmes stedes.
